== ubuzima bwa Kanyombya muri make ==
Kanyombya yavutse kuri mama we Gaudence Mukandutiye na papa we Jean Baptiste Sakumi, avukira mu muryango w'abana 7 gusa hasigaye 5<ref>Kanyombya set to unveil new movie | The New Times | Rwanda <nowiki>https://www.newtimes.co.rw</nowiki> › section › read</ref>. Yize amashuri abanza kuri ecole primaire ste Andre i [[Goma]], akomereza ayisumbuye muri Tuugane Institute ahava muri 1992 ahita ajya mu gisirikare yaje kuvamo muri 2002<ref>Comic Kanyombya in anti-TB campaign | The New Times <nowiki>https://www.newtimes.co.rw</nowiki> › section › read

</ref>. Avuye mugisirikare nibwo yatangiye gukina filimi kugeza nanubu ntiyigeze ahagarara<ref>Sinigeze mbyarana na Kanyombya-Nyinawambogo Yashyize hanze Ukuri {VIDEO} (shafaqna.com)</ref>. Kanyombya ubu afite umugore babanaga nuko baza gusezerana imbere y'amategeko muri 2012 kandi bafitanuye abana 2 ndetse n'abandi barera<ref>Dore ubukwe 10 bwahuruje abantu n'amaherezo yabwo <nowiki>https://www.kigalitoday.com</nowiki> › utuntu-n-utundi › article</ref>
